        <character name="pubescence" value="glabrous" />
        <character name="pubescence" value="villous" modifier="sparsely" />
      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="507.txt-2">
      <text>Phyllaries lanceolate to obovate or oblong, margins ciliate to tomentose, faces glabrous or villous (hairs translucent, whitish or yellowish, sometimes purple-septate), ± stipitate-glandular.</text>
